00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:06,949
♫   Nowhere to escape   ♫

2
00:00:06,949 --> 00:00:09,909
♫   No one to rely on   ♫

3
00:00:09,909 --> 00:00:14,680
♫   Withdrawing smiles   ♫

4
00:00:15,810 --> 00:00:18,819
♫   Never give in   ♫

5
00:00:18,819 --> 00:00:24,700
♫   Forget about one's youth   ♫

6
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:28,869
♫   I've never been afraid of loneliness when 
 embarking on this journey   ♫

7
00:00:28,869 --> 00:00:31,639
♫   Tears and regrets go hand in hand   ♫

8
00:00:31,639 --> 00:00:34,639
♫   But my heart is still fiery-hot   ♫

9
00:00:34,639 --> 00:00:37,690
♫  To the distance  ♫

10
00:00:37,690 --> 00:00:40,659
♫  The miserable past is like a dagger  ♫

11
00:00:40,659 --> 00:00:43,569
♫  Though my wings are broken  ♫

12
00:00:43,569 --> 00:00:50,590
♫  I will keep flying  ♫

13
00:00:52,370 --> 00:00:56,149
♫  Following the direction of the light  ♫

14
00:00:56,149 --> 00:00:58,309
♫  I'll forget you  ♫

15
00:00:58,309 --> 00:01:04,309
♫  The memory shaped my stubbornness  ♫

16
00:01:04,309 --> 00:01:07,309
♫  By virtue of the light in the dark night  ♫

17
00:01:07,309 --> 00:01:10,359
♫  I'll return it with a long ballad  ♫

18
00:01:10,359 --> 00:01:12,319
♫  The river of life is under my feet  ♫

19
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:17,980
♫  I don't regret my craziness  ♫

