All tribes controlled by the Ashile Tribe have this token.

358
00:30:03,699 --> 00:30:04,659
It's a sign of loyalty.

359
00:30:04,660 --> 00:30:06,979
You can even go into Khan's tent with it.

360
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:09,099
You stole your father's token?

361
00:30:09,099 --> 00:30:11,519
We can't get inside without it.

362
00:30:11,519 --> 00:30:15,039
Anyway, I took it from my father. It's not stealing it.

363
00:30:15,039 --> 00:30:16,719
I just borrowed it for a while.

364
00:30:16,719 --> 00:30:18,159
It'll be useless in the future.

365
00:30:18,159 --> 00:30:19,960
Just trash.

366
00:30:22,300 --> 00:30:24,719
Let's go, okay?

